=3D"Fitzgerald Stadium">Fitzgerald Stadium</a>, in Killarney, a capacity of=
 43,180</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MacHale_Park" title=3D"MacHale=
 Park">MacHale Park</a> in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castleb=
ar" title=3D"Castlebar">Castlebar</a>, the largest stadium in Connacht (and=
 in the northern half of the country), a capacity of 42,000</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St_Tiernach%27s_Park" title=3D=
"St Tiernach's Park">St Tiernach's Park</a> in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Clones,_County_Monaghan" title=3D"Clones, County Monaghan">Clo=
nes, County Monaghan</a>, hosts most <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Ulster_Senior_Football_Championship" title=3D"Ulster Senior Football Cha=
mpionship">Ulster</a> finals, a capacity of 36,000</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kingspan_Breffni_Park" class=
=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Kingspan Breffni Park">Kingspan Breffni Park</a>,=
 in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cavan_Town" class=3D"mw-redire=
ct" title=3D"Cavan Town">Cavan Town</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/County_Cavan" title=3D"County Cavan">County Cavan</a>, which hosted =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_rules_football" titl=
e=3D"International rules football">International rules football</a> series =
games in 2013, a capacity of 32,000</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Casement_Park" title=3D"Caseme=
nt Park">Casement Park</a>, in Belfast, which had a capacity of approximate=
ly 31,500 prior to its closure in 2013</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nowlan_Park" title=3D"Nowlan P=
ark">Nowlan Park</a>, in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kilkenny"=
 title=3D"Kilkenny">Kilkenny</a>, a capacity of 27,800</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O%27Moore_Park" title=3D"O'Moo=
re Park">O'Moore Park</a>, in Portlaoise, County Laois, a capacity of 27,00=
0</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Healy_Park" title=3D"Healy Par=
k">Healy Park</a>, in Omagh, County Tyrone, a capacity of 26,500</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pearse_Stadium" title=3D"Pears=
